com.cyc.baseclient.cycobject

Class CycListParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.baseclient.cycobject.CycListParser

  • public class CycListParser
extends Object
    Provides a parser that reads a String representation and constructs the corresponding CycArrayList. Has a weakness in that quoted strings must not contain embedded newlines.
